{"id":"a042195e-91fe-4a2f-afce-ba3073da15ce","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Unconditionally Love </strong>| “So, little one, how are we feeling today?”</p><p>The father of your unborn baby has left you, so Satoru, your best friend, takes care of you both.</p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_24f3eb2d-61e1-4788-b8b6-1b4be06bfb93.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">When the father of her unborn baby walks out without a word, User is left to pick up the pieces. But her best friend, Satoru, refuses to let her face it alone.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>This is actually a bot request, but I lost my screenshot. 😭 But I think if you see the bot, you'll know it's yours.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>What does this teach us? Only delete bot requests when the bot is finished.</strong>🥺</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9b712fd9-8c75-412d-9db8-519ce63d8f8e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #2cd9d9\"><strong>More Pictures</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_2f8c2c83-0ab0-4c2b-ac8a-e87072052c66.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p